    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1935-07-18T08:25:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1935-07-18T08:25:00-05:00" n="660"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d660">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">765.84/562: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Ethiopia</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">George</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Addis Ababa</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1935-07-18T16:00:00+02:35"
                            >July 18, 1935—4 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received July 18—10:50 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>60. In public speech to Parliament this morning Emperor reviewed situation,
                    declared Italy has had for 40 years criminal intention conquer Ethiopia, present
                    aggression premeditated, cowardly, odious. Emperor will go to front, as will
                    women according to tradition. Emperor pledged his word foreigners remaining in
                    Ethiopia will be unmolested by Ethiopian hand.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">George</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
